name: "FISHTAIL" TOP - WHITE
description:
SHIPPING: (Australia Only)

We offer FREE express shipping on orders of $50.00 or more. 
For orders under $50 a flat rate of $10.00  will be charged.
Orders are processed within 24 hours of payment.
Express post will deliver next business day  (Monday to Friday) within Australia. 
Please note: If you are in a red street posting box, or in a remote area it will delay delivery.



RETURNS:

We offer returns on all goods except Sale items and Swimwear. 
You must contact us and return the goods within 14 days of receiving your purchases. 
Shipping returns is at the customers expense.
Goods must be received in their original condition and packaging with their tags.
Refunds will be processed within 5 working days of receipt of the returns.

In the case of faulty goods please contact us within 3 working days of receipt of goods to organise a return. If we find that we are at fault we will organise a refund of the purchases and shipping costs.
